data.description: Don't miss this amazing 4/3/2 on 1 acre in Fox Run! This home boasts an open concept living/kitchen space with beautiful beams in the living room along with a stunning fireplace and vinyl plank flooring. The kitchen is a great size with a breakfast bar and gas stove along with a separate eaten area. You will love the beautiful master bedroom with a master bathroom that has a separate tub and shower and a walk in closet. The other bedrooms are a perfect size for kids, guests, or even an office space. A few of the extras include a mud bench with hooks, a reverse osmosis system, and built in desks. A major bonus to this property is the 30x40 barn with electricity perfect for extra vehicles, entertaining, or storage.
